            <title>[SOLR-11008] TestMetricsHandler.testPropertyFilter failure</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-11008</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This happens pretty frequently - see  &lt;a href=&quot;https://jenkins.thetaphi.de/job/Lucene-Solr-master-Linux/19455/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://jenkins.thetaphi.de/job/Lucene-Solr-master-Linux/19455/&lt;/a&gt; for latest fail.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
